title: Stuck at 33% calculating differences
body: Recently there has been a new update (For Taliyah and others). I attmepted to update my client but it was stuck at 33%. I tried other solutions but it didn't work. It either stayed the same or go to 99% then have an error which made to restart the client again from 33%. I have restarted my computer over 10 times and went onto over 10 websites and videos but none of them worked. I have tried doing this for over 5 hours and now I feel like quitting League. Are there any solutions for this?

replies.body: Hey, this sometimes happens to me too Rice, I would suggest to maybe wait a few hours then try to update again. Good luck :)

Sorry i'm a bit late responding, but if you still are having these issues [please check out this article](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/ysTVIauY-new-having-issues-patching-610-click-here;). It shows the fixes to all the common errors.
